Invertebrates to include in analysis: purple urchin, sunflower sea star, northern kelp crab

## Setup
```{r}
#load necessary packages
library(here)
library(tidyverse)
library(naniar)
library(DHARMa)
library(gtsummary)
library(broom)

#load dataset
inverts <- read_csv("PISCO_kelpforest_swath.1.2.csv")

```

```{r}
#tidy data
inverts <- inverts %>%
  filter(campus == "UCSC",
         classcode %in% c("PUGPRO", "STRPURAD", "PYCHEL")) %>%
  #only include relevant columns for further analysis
  select(campus, survey_year, site, zone, classcode, count, depth)
 
```
